Subject: Worker Job

& [WorkerJob_manual_review] is a turn-spool worker record
  + [worker_id] is manual_review
  + [lane] is manual
  + [objective] is Human review lane for inspecting hub tree and launch commands.
  + [status] is queued
  + [prompt_packet] is prompt.md
  + [launch_command] is not configured
  + [result_file] is result.sop
  + [attention_frame] is none
  = must: inspect launch_command before execution
  - never: infer completion from launch alone
